Singleton class is a class which is having only one instance.
All variables and methods are belongs to only one instance..
Singletonclass concept is usefull for the situation where we want to limit the number of objects for a class..

*Private constructors are used to restrict the instantiation of class.
 if one class nedds to prevent other classes from creating its object then we need private constructors,,
 one of the best example of private constructor is using in singleton class